{"tid":11104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"從1125事件可見香港人都係支那人","createTime":"2016-11-29T07:28:22.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T08:14:59.000Z","uid":25374,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2b7b03283bf0d3992021de097302a6d7d300b887","tid":11104,"uid":25374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T07:28:22.000Z","msg":"班an撚開頭笑住睇IOS用家仆街，以為自己最終會冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇唸過早洩搞得hkg+一樣可以搞鳩你android<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等IOS用家比人趕盡殺絕之後，將來早洩調轉槍頭對付an撚果時重有邊個為你地抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以香港人承傳左支那人鍾意內鬥鬼打鬼，唔團體落井下石既劣質基因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好彩an撚係最後關頭識得痛改前非過檔與我地同一陣線一齊對付方仗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望以後大家可以和平共處，唔好再分android同IOS咁on鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6df3fcb6fd97ec678cfeed1d3ec73eeecfbfb17","tid":11104,"uid":25374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T07:31:41.000Z","msg":"因為用唔同電話而分黨分派既，全世界可能得支那人先會咁on鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4aad159be1e811cb0149499d21af47cbc871b16","tid":11104,"uid":25374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T07:34:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbf2ab437a0cdb531ae7bbdb094b3523907b5152","tid":11104,"uid":25374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T07:59:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b71b49f61a4e8cfedb353029cd23b384f1060e0","tid":11104,"uid":16528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T08:01:04.000Z","msg":"咁都可以話到香港人係支那人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 青好波"},{"pid":"413454640a6b7ab64c8ef20da25e6642b60e